summary:
FINOM offers a comprehensive online banking solution designed specifically for freelancers, entrepreneurs, and SMEs, seamlessly integrating banking, accounting, and financial management solutions. 
Join us as a valued partner, simplify your customers' financial lives and unlock your new revenue streams through attractive incentives we offer for partners.
Let's build the future of simplified digital banking together!

Our hassle-free banking experience includes: 
- Fast 100% online account opening with an European IBAN,
- A complimentary 3-months subscription with no hidden costs,
- The convenience of debit cards (both physical and virtual) with up to 3% cashback,
- Multi-banking capabilities and real-time expense management,
- Simple invoicing and reconciliation system.
